description: Resource this agent is associated with
Internal identifier. Ideally fill out acronym for an organisation and full name for a person, otherwise an identifier is automatically generated
Type of agent: person or organisation

Organisation name from Research Organization Registry (ROR). If your organisation is not listed, please look up in ROR registry: https://ror.org/ and add ROR identifier in 'pid' field below. ROR typically lists only top level organisations. For instance, if you want to fill out a department within an organisation, find the top level organisation name in ROR and fill that out. Then fill out department name in the 'department' field below.
If your organisation is not listed, please look up in ROR id: https://ror.org/.
Organisation name if not listed above, ideally from ROR: https://ror.org/
Name of department within the organisation
Type(s) of contribution or role in the resource
Whether the organisation is the lead organisation of this resource
